  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM7.8">
<l>muḻutum veṇṇe yaḷaintutoṭ ṭuṇṇum mukiḻi ḷañciṟut tāmaraik kaiyum</l>
<l>eḻilkoḷ tāmpukoṇ ṭaṭippataṟ keḷku nilaiyum veṇtayir tōyntacev vāyum</l>
<l>aḻukai yumañci nōkkumaṉ ṉōkku maṇikoḷ ceñciṟu vāyneḷip patuvum</l>
<l>toḻukai yumivai kaṇṭa vacōtai tollai yiṉpat tiṟutikaṇ ṭāḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Yaśodā who saw these –</l>
<l rend="indent">[Your] little tender budding lotus[-like] hands that take hold of and eat the butter,</l>
<l rend="indent">having wholly mixed [it] up,</l>
<l rend="indent">the state of fear at [her] striking [You] with the beautiful cord,</l>
<l rend="indent">[Your] red mouth filled with white curds,</l>
<l rend="indent">[Your] crying,</l>
<l rend="indent">that glance given fearing [her],</l>
<l rend="indent">[Your] twisting [Your] beautiful, small, red lips,</l>
<l rend="indent">and [Your] worshipping [gesture] -</l>
<l>saw the bounds of great happiness.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
